<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Check-in Recorded - Eighteen</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #4361EE;
      --primary-dark: #3A0CA3;
      --accent: #F72585;
      --light: #F8F9FA;
      --dark: #212529;
      --success: #4CC9F0;
      --gray: #6C757D;
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    
    body {
      background-color: var(--light);
      color: var(--dark);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .logo h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    
    .success-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background-color: #4CC9F0;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 40px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.3);
    }
    
    .message-box {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 20px 0 40px 0;
    }
    
    .message-box h2 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .message-box p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 20px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: var(--primary-dark);
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>Eighteen</h1>
      <p>The Habit Launchpad</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="message-box">
      <div class="success-icon">âœ“</div>
      <h2>Success!</h2>
      <p>Your check-in has been recorded.</p>
      <p>Keep up the good work!</p>
      <p>Remember, it takes 18 days to form a neural pathway that makes your habit automatic.</p>
      
      <a href="/" class="btn">Return Home</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Based on habit formation research by Phillippa Lally et al., UCL</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>